    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/6d8da1d12ba7a4b30dda3b8d0f92a2eb.avif?t=1754239358\" width=225 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ankhway</strong>  it's a 2D Indie <i>Adventure</i> and <i>Sci-fi</i> videogame with an <i>epic, original and intriguing</i> story that incorporates systems like jumping to avoid traps such as spikes, shooting, ''<i><strong>MP3 Player</strong></i>'' Item to listen to the soundtrack <strong>completely free</strong> in-game... Among many other mechanics and game systems! Combining the adventure (Exploration, puzzle-solving etc) with action and science fiction.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>NEO-RETRO MODERN PIXEL ART STYLE GRAPHICS</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features gorgeous, colorful hand-drawn <i>pixel art</i> by awesome artists like <i><strong>Rinober</strong></i><strong>, <i>KR</i> or <i>NeonPixel</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/24c67f777e673132ec1e91ff98c5cb61.poster.avif?t=1754239358\" width=550 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/24c67f777e673132ec1e91ff98c5cb61.webm?t=1754239358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/24c67f777e673132ec1e91ff98c5cb61.mp4?t=1754239358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/07f079424c14e672a19d1fd92632135a.avif?t=1754239358\" width=280 height=80 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In a remote and wild area of the Sahara Desert <br>an adventurer expert in Hieroglyphs and history<br>of Egypt has just discovered something that would <br>change many more things you could never think about.<br><br><br>After days of working to dig everything up, he discovers<br>what turns out to be some underground ruins, a small<br>pyramid and a sphinx in perfect condition, thus revealing <br>its face. In addition, a strange opening but in the ground, <br>so the pyramid seems inaccessible and it seems like it <br>acts as an antenna, it's located at the top of what <br>appears to be the entrance to some secret passages.<br><br><br>The Egyptian government seems astonished but nervous and<br>scared, they somehow know that the adventurous explorer<br>is going to get into the underground ruins to explore <br>this unknown place.<br><br><br><br>After arduous discussions, he managed to get them to leave him, <br>however, they feel responsible for what may happen to him and <br>they will wait at the exit.<br><br><br><br>This can certainly be the beginning of his great adventure...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/c1fc1efe1f22b0e59f33a8058fcb93ce.avif?t=1754239358\" width=280 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Melee Weapons:</strong></i></u></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/54d7ef39357e9428aae2b698a5797c3f.poster.avif?t=1754239358\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/54d7ef39357e9428aae2b698a5797c3f.webm?t=1754239358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/54d7ef39357e9428aae2b698a5797c3f.mp4?t=1754239358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Shooting System:</strong></i></u></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/a39cb192af89363559fded3b44bde579.poster.avif?t=1754239358\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/a39cb192af89363559fded3b44bde579.webm?t=1754239358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/a39cb192af89363559fded3b44bde579.mp4?t=1754239358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong><u>Sprint and Stamina:</u></strong></i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/7194fd2abbd93c6eb58fc5ab88ab1344.poster.avif?t=1754239358\" width=652 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/7194fd2abbd93c6eb58fc5ab88ab1344.webm?t=1754239358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=