class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/e4a92b9f05ffd1a89388c78852aa1a57.poster.avif?t=1754239358\" width=420 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/e4a92b9f05ffd1a89388c78852aa1a57.webm?t=1754239358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/e4a92b9f05ffd1a89388c78852aa1a57.mp4?t=1754239358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong><u>Exploration:</u></strong></i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/852c57363d46b13c558478a8eb9e7af5.poster.avif?t=1754239358\" width=664 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/852c57363d46b13c558478a8eb9e7af5.webm?t=1754239358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/852c57363d46b13c558478a8eb9e7af5.mp4?t=1754239358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Variety of unique and highly detailed scenarios:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/02892feb66857567f20d6b14f98ff68d.poster.avif?t=1754239358\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/02892feb66857567f20d6b14f98ff68d.webm?t=1754239358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/02892feb66857567f20d6b14f98ff68d.mp4?t=1754239358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong><u>Diagonal </u></strong></i><strong><u>Movement<i>/Jump and Smooth and Precise Pixel-Based Movement:</i></u></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/13590b08ec4a26c8405056ffc01e10e6.poster.avif?t=1754239358\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/13590b08ec4a26c8405056ffc01e10e6.webm?t=1754239358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/13590b08ec4a26c8405056ffc01e10e6.mp4?t=1754239358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Puzzle Solving:</strong></i></u></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/60a0268771f346f9b977aae0086298ae.poster.avif?t=1754239358\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/60a0268771f346f9b977aae0086298ae.webm?t=1754239358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/60a0268771f346f9b977aae0086298ae.mp4?t=1754239358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>EPIC</strong></i><strong> SOUNDTRACK:</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Made by talented composers like <i><strong>Joel Steulder, Aaron Lucas or Elektrobear</strong></i>. Listen to the soundtrack in-game with the item ''<strong>MP3 Player</strong>''!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/1d3278c4ae7908c94cc47221fdc70fbd.poster.avif?t=1754239358\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/1d3278c4ae7908c94cc47221fdc70fbd.webm?t=1754239358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190510/extras/1d3278c4ae7908c94cc47221fdc70fbd.mp4?t=1754239358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>~ The videogame contains non-realistic violence (Pixel art) such as blood, shooting and moderately vulgar language; occasional swear words.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  ☥𓂀𓂀𓂀𓋹𓁈𓃠𓆃☥𓅓𓆣</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >IT'S THE <i>TIME</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >IT'S YOUR <i>DESTINY</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragra